trpzBasic.name: trpzBasic

trpzSerialNumber.name: trpzSerialNumber
trpzSerialNumber.description: The serial number of the switch.

trpzSwMajorVersionNumber.name: trpzSwMajorVersionNumber
trpzSwMajorVersionNumber.description: The major release version of the running software.

trpzSwMinorVersionNumber.name: trpzSwMinorVersionNumber
trpzSwMinorVersionNumber.description: The minor release version of the running software.

trpzVersionString.name: trpzVersionString
trpzVersionString.description: The version string of the running software, including the major, minor, patch and build numbers, such as 3.0.0.185

trpzMobilityDomainName.name: trpzMobilityDomainName
trpzMobilityDomainName.description: The mobility domain containing the switch, or a zero-length string when the mobility domain is unknown.

trpzMobilitySeedIp.name: trpzMobilitySeedIp
trpzMobilitySeedIp.description: The IPv4 address of the seed switch for this switch's mobility domain, or the IPv4 address 0.0.0.0 if unknown.

trpzMobilityMemberTableSize.name: trpzMobilityMemberTableSize
trpzMobilityMemberTableSize.description: The number of entries in the mobility member table, trpzMobilityMemberTable.

trpzMobilityMemberTable.name: trpzMobilityMemberTable
trpzMobilityMemberTable.description: Table of members of the mobility domain, indexed by the member IPv4 address.

trpzMobilityMemberEntry.name: trpzMobilityMemberEntry
trpzMobilityMemberEntry.description: An entry in the trpzMobilityMemberTable table.

trpzMobilityMemberEntryAddr.name: trpzMobilityMemberEntryAddr
trpzMobilityMemberEntryAddr.description: IPv4 address of a member of the mobility domain.

trpzLicenseInfoTableSize.name: trpzLicenseInfoTableSize
trpzLicenseInfoTableSize.description: The number of entries in the license table, trpzLicenseInfoTable.

trpzLicenseInfoTable.name: trpzLicenseInfoTable
trpzLicenseInfoTable.description: Table of installed licenses on the switch. The licences provide additional capabilities over the default capabilities of the switch.

trpzLicenseInfoEntryValue.name: trpzLicenseInfoEntryValue
trpzLicenseInfoEntryValue.description: The value of the feature enabled, for example a feature may have multiple levels of licensing, so the value will very with the license level.

trpzLicenseInfoEntryDescr.name: trpzLicenseInfoEntryDescr
trpzLicenseInfoEntryDescr.description: A human interpretable description of this license, for example, '120 APs or DAPs.'
